Package: rcces
Version: 1.0.1
Title: Helper Functions for CCES Representation Projects
Authors@R: person("Shiro", "Kuriwaki", email = "shirokuriwaki@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Functions to format, clean, and operationalize variables used in
  Shiro Kuriwaki's CCES-based representation research. Includes replication functions for
  reshaping survey responses, computing dyadic agreement between constituents
  and legislators, aggregating opinion to geographic units, labeling Stata
  variables, and writing formatted numbers for LaTeX output.
Imports:
  dplyr,
  glue,
  haven,
  lifecycle,
